text:
🌅Punggol Promenade Riverside Walk connects Punggol Promenade Nature Walk to Sungei Serangoon Park Connector.
🚤A scenic Walk along  the riverbank of Sungei Serangoon, passing by Sunrise Bridge, Sunrise Boardwalk, Lor Halus Red Bridge, Pasir Ris Bridge, Rest Stop, Eateries, Fitness Corner and Scenic Stop.
🍂📹An idyllic hike with many photography apportunities.
